{"tid":1821690,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個自我膨脹嘅時間","createTime":"2020-01-12T13:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T15:44:37.000Z","uid":205742,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3aa0cb61fa32729ced794e5812be063dd152d51e","tid":1821690,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:06:26.000Z","msg":"同一時間俾五條女鍾意緊，成日郁啲就約我或者噓寒問暖，有個內儉啲嘅就係靠佢望住我嘅眼神發現<br />\n<br />\n等我嗰期真係以為自己好有型好靚仔，成日出街都chok住行路，諗住自己係女都吸引到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好景不常，依家折墮到冇人鍾意不特只，仲要個人頹到所有人都唔想理我，鍾意我嘅人因愛成恨<br />\n<br />\n好傷心 覺得好多野都打回原形咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7f55d473a77ec0c611373e7bdf53b5fc8192f9","tid":1821690,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:10:56.000Z","msg":"好多人追既靚女miss跪係到幫自己含個一刻"},{"pid":"4de50a732b0481d926234fec16467a201a336d3a","tid":1821690,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d7f55d473a77ec0c611373e7bdf53b5fc8192f9","tid":1821690,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:10:56.000Z","msg":"好多人追既靚女miss跪係到幫自己含個一刻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"Miss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64641f256a502a9abbd2cc38eba8f6883593b5e9","tid":1821690,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d7f55d473a77ec0c611373e7bdf53b5fc8192f9","tid":1821690,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:10:56.000Z","msg":"好多人追既靚女miss跪係到幫自己含個一刻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/a/ad/RGyHYs9.gif/revision/latest/top-crop/width/220/height/220?cb=20151222170602\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia